{"tid":969862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人可以咁撚無品？","createTime":"2019-01-05T11:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T15:07:05.000Z","uid":138539,"like":11,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd37ca556a4b7a5cae44f3ad35c68fbdabb5ad7","tid":969862,"uid":138539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩去行uniqlo<br />\n睇緊衫既時候 望到有兩個人係度試緊褸<br />\n然後佢地係係個架拎完件褸試完<br />\n就咁掉返係對面既貨架<br />\n然後就變左下圖既情況<br />\n對面個貨架堆滿晒佢試既褸<br />\n見到嗰下即刻話佢有冇搞錯咁樣整亂人地啲架<br />\n但佢地只係扮聽唔到 然後仲要施施然講左句 喂去隔離試下啲褲 然後由啲褸咁樣放係度就行左去<br />\n<br />\n即係你係客唔係大晒<br />\n買唔買野都好 都唔應該咁樣整亂人地既貨架<br />\n點解可以咁無品然後仲要覺得自己無問題？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/a/yxsK79r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FyxsK79r&h=de25b3e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23721b26c8a4873db7a25f565b40045a5f05473c","tid":969862,"uid":138539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T11:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/osPBTzp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FosPBTzp.jpg&h=43b49b86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似出唔到圖 補返"},{"pid":"6777973cb9b86978ea9d33699b2a622281062095","tid":969862,"uid":161374,"like":5,"dislike":25,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:03:59.000Z","msg":"好正常<br />\n<br />\n唔亂點會請咁多人，人地因你好手尾比人炒咗點算？<br />\n<br />\n自己都大把衫未執，點解出街仲要幫人地鋪頭執"},{"pid":"991475d0c60297dd1747a6dc839fbe1a28db6ab2","tid":969862,"uid":195887,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"我出埋你份糧"},{"pid":"c91efcba2b6088a57fc8f1accfc6528d97629f62","tid":969862,"uid":223084,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-05T13:08:44.000Z","msg":"服裝店請人就係幫人摺衫執衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef48ccfbf405d0f7854d3b9742d31af4b3d8fae0","tid":969862,"uid":194894,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":